These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: cherry, potato, pomegranate
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, family, thriller
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, italian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, dog
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, skateboard
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the canadian##1
5. the italian is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person eating cherry is between the owner of the snake and the person eating potato##2
8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | soy-milk      | lemonade      |
| Food          | potato   | cherry   | pomegranate       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | horror | family    |
| Nationality   | chinese  | canadian    | italian    |
| Pet           | turtle    | dog    | snake |
| Transport     | car  | skateboard     | boat        |

