.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, cranberry, artichoke
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, adventure
There are 3 different nationalities: french, egyptian, japanese
3 different pets are kept: lizard, horse, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, swimming
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the person eating artichoke is between the japanese and the person drinking iced-tea##2
7. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite     | soy-milk        | iced-tea      |
| Food          | cranberry    | artichoke       | blueberry  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | disaster | spy    |
| Nationality   | japanese | french   | egyptian    |
| Pet           | horse      | lizard  | fish      |
| Sport         | swimming    | weightlifting      | climbing |

