.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, lime, pepper
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, ambient
There are 3 different nationalities: german, canadian, colombian
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, turtle
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the colombian and the owner of the hedgehog##2
2. the canadian is on the left of the german##1
3. the german is the german##1
4. the owner of the turtle is the fan of blues##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating kiwi##2
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | kiwi  | lime    | pepper   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | skydiving | chess |
| Music-Genre   | ambient       | blues    | dubstep |
| Nationality   | colombian    | canadian  | german  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | turtle   | hedgehog       |
| Transport     | roller | jet-ski     | scooter       |

