There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish, chinese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sprite-polo, handball, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, trike
1. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the trike is the brazilian##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the chinese is on the right of the spanish##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person eating peas and the person driving the skateboard##2
9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | sprite     | soy-milk      |
| Food          | peas     | nectarine     | corn     |
| Hobby         | traveling      | singing | writing    |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | spanish | chinese     |
| Sport         | sprite-polo   | handball      | surfing |
| Transport     | trike | tram      | skateboard          |

