The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, adventure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, metal, classical
There are 3 different nationalities: american, russian, brazilian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
4. the russian is on the far right##1
5. the fan of jazz is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the chef is between the person eating cucumber and the owner of the goldfish##2
7. the american is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
8. the lawyer is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |      2       |       3       |
| Food          | apricot           | blueberry       | cucumber       |
| Job           | doctor | chef    | lawyer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific      | time-travel | adventure        |
| Music-Genre   | metal          | classical        | jazz       |
| Nationality   | brazilian        | american     | russian      |
| Pet           | goldfish           | chinchilla   | ferret           |

