The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, iced-tea-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, roller
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is iced-tea-polo##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person driving the roller is between the person eating lime and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
8. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's sport is iced-tea-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage    | mirinda      | lemonade     | iced-tea       |
| Food        | onion | lettuce  | lime |
| Hobby       | woodworking   | hiking     | traveling     |
