.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, documentary
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, d&b, reggae
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, tennis, lacrosse
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, car, train
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the van and the owner of the goldfish##2
3. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan of folk##1
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
